author: Zach Berman
title: Ryan Mathews active for Eagles; Odell Beckham Jr. active for Giants
text: Eagles Ryan Mathews active for Eagles; Odell Beckham Jr. active for Giants The good news for the Eagles is that running back Ryan Mathews is active for Monday night's game against the New York Giants. The bad news is that wide receiver Odell Beckham Jr. is active for the Giants. Ryan Mathews active for Eagles; Odell Beckham Jr. active for Giants
